@startuml Use Case Diagram - Guitarclassbynde
title Use Case Diagram — Guitarclassbynde

left to right direction
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
}
skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #E2E8F0
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF7ED
  BorderColor #C2410C
}

actor "Tamu" as Guest
actor "Peserta Didik" as Student
actor "Admin" as Admin

rectangle "Sistem Guitarclassbynde" {
  together {
    usecase "Login" as UC_Login
    usecase "Registrasi" as UC_Register
    usecase "Verifikasi email" as UC_Verify
    usecase "Logout" as UC_Logout
  }

  together {
    usecase "Lihat dan pilih kelas" as UC_Browse
    usecase "Kelola profil" as UC_Profile
    usecase "Melakukan pembayaran" as UC_Pay
  }

  together {
    usecase "Akses materi video" as UC_Video
    usecase "Ikuti tutorial lagu" as UC_Song
    usecase "Lihat progress belajar" as UC_Progress
    usecase "Melihat jadwal sesi" as UC_Schedule
    usecase "Mendaftar sesi coaching" as UC_Book
    usecase "Melihat status booking" as UC_Status
    usecase "Melakukan sesi videocall" as UC_Call
  }

  usecase "Buat dan kelola\nsesi coaching" as UC_AdminCoach
}

Guest --> UC_Login
Guest --> UC_Register

Student --> UC_Verify
Student --> UC_Browse
Student --> UC_Profile
Student --> UC_Pay
Student --> UC_Video
Student --> UC_Song
Student --> UC_Progress
Student --> UC_Schedule
Student --> UC_Book
Student --> UC_Status
Student --> UC_Call
Student --> UC_Logout

Admin --> UC_Login
Admin --> UC_Logout
Admin --> UC_AdminCoach

' Fitur konten & coaching: wajib melalui konteks "sudah berbayar" (satu gelembung pembayaran)
UC_Video ..> UC_Pay : <<include>>
UC_Song ..> UC_Pay : <<include>>
UC_Progress ..> UC_Pay : <<include>>
UC_Schedule ..> UC_Pay : <<include>>
UC_Book ..> UC_Pay : <<include>>
UC_Status ..> UC_Pay : <<include>>
UC_Call ..> UC_Pay : <<include>>

note as N1
  **<<include>> ke Melakukan pembayaran** di sini bermaksud:
  fitur tersebut **hanya dipakai jika** pengguna sudah
  menyelesaikan pembayaran / punya hak akses dari transaksi
  (bukan artinya setiap buka video sistem menagih ulang).
  **Lihat kelas** & **Kelola profil** tidak di-include ke bayar:
  bisa dipakai sebelum atau tanpa langganan penuh, sesuai kebijakan produk.
end note

note bottom of UC_Logout
  **Precondition:** pengguna sedang terautentikasi.
end note

@enduml
